Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> if the app is enabled; otherwise, <code>false</code>. Setting this value to false disables the app (takes the app offline).

Enabled hostnames for the app.Hostnames need to be assigned (see HostNames) AND enabled. Otherwise, the app is not served on those hostnames.

reserved
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> if reserved; otherwise, <code>false</code>.

Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

Last time the app was modified, in UTC. Read-only.

Configuration of the app.

IList<String> IList(Of String)

Azure Traffic Manager hostnames associated with the app. Read-only.

premiumAppDeployed
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

Indicates whether app is deployed as a premium app.

scmSiteAlsoStopped
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to stop SCM (KUDU) site when the app is stopped; otherwise, <code>false</code>. The default is <code>false</code>.

targetSwapSlot
String String

Specifies which deployment slot this app will swap into. Read-only.

hostingEnvironmentProfile
HostingEnvironmentProfile HostingEnvironmentProfile

App Service Environment to use for the app.

microService
String String

Micro services like apps, logic apps.

gatewaySiteName
String String

Name of gateway app associated with the app.

clientAffinityEnabled
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to enable client affinity; <code>false</code> to stop sending session affinity cookies, which route client requests in the same session to the same instance. Default is <code>true</code>.

clientCertEnabled
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to enable client certificate authentication (TLS mutual authentication); otherwise, <code>false</code>. Default is <code>false</code>.

hostNamesDisabled
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> to disable the public hostnames of the app; otherwise, <code>false</code>. If <code>true</code>, the app is only accessible via API management process.

outboundIpAddresses
String String

List of IP addresses that the app uses for outbound connections (e.g. database access). Read-only.

containerSize
Nullable<Int32> Nullable(Of Int32)

Size of the function container.

dailyMemoryTimeQuota
Nullable<Int32> Nullable(Of Int32)

Maximum allowed daily memory-time quota (applicable on dynamic apps only).

suspendedTill
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

App suspended till in case memory-time quota is exceeded.

maxNumberOfWorkers
Nullable<Int32> Nullable(Of Int32)

Maximum number of workers. This only applies to Functions container.

cloningInfo
CloningInfo CloningInfo

If specified during app creation, the app is cloned from a source app.

resourceGroup
String String

Name of the resource group the app belongs to. Read-only.

isDefaultContainer
Nullable<Boolean> Nullable(Of Boolean)

<code>true</code> if the app is a default container; otherwise, <code>false</code>.

defaultHostName
String String

Default hostname of the app. Read-only.

slotSwapStatus
SlotSwapStatus SlotSwapStatus

Status of the last deployment slot swap operation.
